---
description: Bump graph pack version when ingest wire or sources change
globs: discovery/harvest/**,pipeline/ned/**,graph/ingest/**,pkg/harvest/**,pkg/commit/**,docs/schemas/**
alwaysApply: false
---

# Ingest changes → graph pack version

When editing files matched by this rule:

1. Update matching JSON in [docs/schemas/](../../docs/schemas/) if `pkg/harvest` or `pkg/commit` types changed.
2. Before commit, run `./scripts/release/bump-graph-version.sh patch` (updates [versions.env](../../versions.env)).
3. Run `make check-graph-version` to verify the bump is present.
4. If graph output changed materially, rebuild and publish per [docs/contracts/graph-pack.md](../../docs/contracts/graph-pack.md).

Ingest-affecting paths only — changes to `knowledge/serve/` or deploy-only files do not require a graph pack bump unless they alter ingest behavior.
